\c 15
\s Nhaka yaJudha
\p
\v 1 Zvino mujenya werudzi rwevana vaJudha nemhuri dzavo waiva pamuganhu waEdhomu\x + Num.. 34.3.\x*, renje reZini nechekuchamhembe\x + Num.. 33.36.\x* kumacheto kwechamhembe\x + 12.3.\x*.
\v 2 Uye muganhu wavo wekuchamhembe waiva kubva pamacheto egungwa remunyu, kubva panopinda gungwa munyika pakatarisa nechekuchamhembe\x + Num.. 34.3.\x*;
\v 3 ndokubudira kuchamhembe kumukwidza weAkirabhimi, ndokupfuurira kuZini, ndokukwira kubva kuchamhembe kuenda kuKadheshi-Bharineya, ndokupfuurira kuHezironi, ndokukwira kuAdhari, ndokudzokera paKarika\x + 15.47. Num.. 34.5.\x*;
\v 4 ndokupfuurira kuAzimoni\x + 15.47. Num.. 34.5.\x*, ndokubudira kurwizi rweEgipita; nekubuda kwemuganhu kwaiva pagungwa. Uyu uchava muganhu wenyu wekuchamhembe.
\v 5 Zvino muganhu wekumabvazuva waiva gungwa remunyu kusvika kumacheto aJoridhani. Nemuganhu parutivi rwemaodzanyemba waiva kubva panopinda gungwa munyika kubva pamacheto aJoridhani.
\v 6 Zvino muganhu wakakwira kuBheti-Hogira\x + 18.19,21.\x*, ndokupfuurira kumaodzanyemba kweBheti-Arabha\x + 18.18,22; 15.61.\x*; muganhu ndokukwira kubwe raBhohani mwanakomana waRubheni\x + 18.17; 15.37.\x*.
\v 7 Zvino muganhu wakakwira wakananga kuDhebhiri\x + 15.15.\x*, kubva pamupata weAkori\x + 7.26.\x*, uye nechekumaodzanyemba wakatarisa kuGirigari, riri pamberi pemukwidza weAdhumimi\x + 18.17; 15.37.\x*, riri kuchamhembe kwerwizi. Zvino muganhu wakapfuurira kusvika kumvura yeEni-Shemeshi\x + 18.17; 15.37.\x*; uye kubuda kwawo kwaiva kusvika paEni-Rogeri\x + 18.16. 2 Sam. 17.17. 1 Madz. 1.9.\x*.
\v 8 Zvino muganhu wakakwira nemupata wemwanakomana waHinomi\x + 18.16. 2 Madz. 23.10. 2 Makor. 28.3. Jer. 7.31,32. 19.2,6.\x* kusvika kurutivi rweVaJebhusi kuchamhembe rwunova Jerusarema\x + 15.63.\x*; muganhu ndokukwira kusvika pamusoro wegomo riri pamberi pemupata weHinomi nechekumavirazuva\x + 17.15.\x*, uri pamacheto emupata weVaRefaimu nechekumaodzanyemba\x + 17.15.\x*.
\v 9 Zvino muganhu wakamonereka kubva pamusoro pegomo kusvika kuchitubu chemvura yeNefitoa\x + 18.15.\x*, ndokubudira kumaguta egomo reEfuroni; muganhu ndokumonereka kusvika kuBhaara\x + 15.11,29,60; 19.44; 2 Sam. 6.2. 1 Makor. 13.5,6.\x* rinova Kiriati-Jearimi\x + 9.17.\x*.
\v 10 Muganhu ndokutenderera kubva paBhaara nechekumavirazuva kusvika pagomo reSeiri, ndokupfuurira kurutivi rwegomo reJearimi kubva kumaodzanyemba, rinova Kesaroni, ndokuburukira kuBheti-Shemeshi\x + 21.16. 19.22,38. 1 Sam. 6.9,12. 2 Madz. 14.11. 2 Makor. 25.21,23; 28.18.\x*, ndokupfuurira kuTimuna\x + 15.57. 19.43. Gen.. 38.12,13. Vato. 14.1,5; 2 Makor. 28.18.\x*.
\v 11 Zvino muganhu wakabudira kurutivi rweEkironi nechekumaodzanyemba\x + 15.45,46. 13.3. 19.43. Vato. 1.18. 1 Sam. 5.10. 6.17. 7.14. 2 Madz. 1.2,3,6,16. Amo. 1.8. Zef. 2.4. Zek. 9.5.\x*; muganhu ndokumonereka kusvika paShikeroni, ndokupfuurira kugomo reBhaara\x + 15.9.\x*, ndokubudira Jabhuneeri; uye kubuda kwemuganhu kwaiva pagungwa.
\v 12 Zvino muganhu wekumavirazuva \add wai\add*svika kugungwa guru nemuganhu \add waro\x + 15.47. 23.4. Num.. 34.6,7. Eze. 47.20. Det. 11.24. 34.2.\x*\add*. Uyu muganhu wevana vaJudha kunhivi dzose nemhuri dzavo.
\p
\v 13 Zvino kuna Karebhu mwanakomana waJefune\x + 14.13-15.\x* wakapa mugove pakati pevana vaJudha, zvichienderana nemurairo waJehovha kuna Joshua: Kiriyati-Aribha, baba vaAnaki, rinova Hebhuroni.
\v 14 Karebhu ndokudzinga panhaka vanakomana vatatu vaAnaki kubvapo: Sheshai naAhimani naTarimai, zvizvarwa zvaAnaki\x + Num.. 13.22. Vato. 1.10,20.\x*.
\v 15 Zvino wakakwira kubvapo kuenda kuvagari veDhebhiri\x + 15.49; 10.38.\x*. Zvino zita reDhebhiri pakutanga raiva Kiriati-Seferi.
\p
\v 16 Karebhu ndokuti\x + 15.19, Vato. 1.12-15. 1 Sam. 17.25.\x*: Anorova Kiriati-Seferi ndokuritapa, ndichapa kwaari mukunda wangu Akisa ave mukadzi.
\v 17 Zvino Otiniyeri mwanakomana waKenazi\x + Num.. 32.12; 14.6,14.\x* munin'ina waKarebhu wakaritapa; iye ndokumupa mukunda wake Akisa kuva mukadzi.
\v 18 Zvino zvakaitika paaisvika, kuti wakamukurudzira kukumbira munda kuna baba vake; zvino wakaburuka pambongoro\x + Gen..24.64; 1 Sam. 25.23.\x*; Karebhu ndokuti kwaari: Chii \add chandingaita\add* kwauri?
\v 19 Iye ndokuti: Ndipei ropafadzo\x + Gen.. 33.11; Josh. 14.13.\x*; sezvamakandipa nyika yekuchamhembe, ndipeiwo zvitubu zvemvura. Zvino wakamupa zvitubu zvekumusoro nezvitubu zvepazasi\x + Gen.. 21.25; 26.15,18-20.\x*.
\p
\v 20 Iyi inhaka yerudzi rwevana vaJudha nemhuri dzavo.
\v 21 Zvino maguta ekumacheto erudzi rwevana vaJudha kusvika kumuganhu waEdhomu nechekuchamhembe aiva Kabhezeeri\x + 1 Makor. 11.22. Neh. 11.25.\x*, neEdheri\x + Gen.. 35.21.\x*, neJaguri,
